 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
 SmsHosting Plugin for Roundcube
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------

 Plugin that adds a possibility to send sms message via smshosting.it gateway

 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
 
 1. 	Configuration
 2.		Database
 
 1. Configuration
 ----------------

 Copy config.inc.php.dist to config.inc.php and set the options as described
 within the file.


 2. Database (mysql)
 ----------------
 
 Execute update.sql file in the database folder to add smshosting configuration field for the roundcube identity schema 